19:29   Ubwo Imana yarimburaga imidugudu yo muri icyo kibaya, yibutse Aburahamu, yohereza Loti ngo ave muri iryo tsembwa, ubwo yatsembaga imidugudu Loti yari atuyemo.
19:30 Loti ava i Sowari, arazamuka ajya ku musozi, abanayo n'abakobwa be bombi kuko yatinyaga gutura i Sowari, abana n'abakobwa be bombi mu buvumo. 
19:31 Uw'imfura abwira murumuna we ati “Data arashaje, kandi nta muntu mu isi wo kuturongora nk'uko abo mu isi bose bakora. 
