20:1 Aburahamu avayo agenda yerekeje i Negebu, atura hagati y'i Kadeshi n'i Shuri, asuhukira i Gerari. 
20:2  Aburahamu avuga Sara umugore we ati “Ni mushiki wanjye”, Abimeleki umwami w'i Gerari atumira Sara aramujyana. 
20:3  Maze Imana ibonekerera Abimeleki mu nzozi nijoro, iramubwira iti “Umeze nk'intumbi ku bwa wa mugore wenze, kuko afite umugabo.”
20:4 Ariko Abimeleki yari ataramwegera, arayibaza ati “Mwami, wakwica ishyanga nubwo rikiranuka? 
20:5  Ubwe si we wavuze ati ‘Ni mushiki wanjye’? N'umugore na we ubwe ntiyavuze ati ‘Ni musaza wanjye’? Icyo nkoze icyo, ngikoze mfite umutima ukiranutse n'amaboko atanduye.”
20:6 Imana imusubiriza mu nzozi iti “Koko nzi yuko ukoze ibyo ufite umutima ukiranutse, kandi nanjye nakubujije kuncumuraho, ni cyo cyatumye ntagukundira kumukoraho. 
20:7   Noneho subiza uwo mugabo umugore we, kuko ari umuhanuzi, azagusabira ukarama. Ariko nutamumusubiza, umenye yuko utazabura gupfana n'abawe bose.”
20:8 Abimeleki azinduka kare kare, ahamagaza abagaragu be bose, abatekerereza ibyo byose, baratinya cyane. 
20:9 Maze Abimeleki ahamagaza Aburahamu aramubaza ati “Watugize ibiki? Nagucumuyeho iki, cyatumye unshyiraho jyewe n'ubwami bwanjye icyaha gikomeye? Wankoreye ibidakwiriye gukorwa.” 
20:10  Abimeleki arongera abaza Aburahamu ati “Wabonye iki cyagukoresheje ibyo?”
20:11 Aburahamu aramusubiza ati “Ni uko nibwiraga ntashidikanya yuko aha hantu nta kubaha Imana guhari, kandi nanjye nari nzi ko bazanyica bampora umugore wanjye. 
20:12 Erega ni mushiki wanjye, ni mwene data, ariko si mwene mama, kandi koko naramurongoye. 
20:13  Kandi ubwo Imana yankuraga mu nzu ya data ikanzerereza, naramubwiye nti ‘Iyo ni yo neza uzajya ungirira, aho tuzajya tugera hose ujye uvuga yuko ndi musaza wawe.’ ”
20:14 Abimeleki azana intama n'inka n'abagaragu n'abaja, abiha Aburahamu, amusubiza na Sara umugore we. 
20:15 Abimeleki aramubwira ati “Igihugu cyanjye kiri imbere yawe, uture aho uzashaka hose.” 
20:16  Abwira na Sara ati “Dore mpaye musaza wawe ibice by'ifeza igihumbi, ni byo bizaba ibyo gukinga mu maso y'abo muri kumwe bose, ngukuyeho umugayo imbere ya bose.”
20:17 Aburahamu asaba Imana, ikiza Abimeleki n'umugore we n'abaja be, barabyara. 
20:18 Kuko Uwiteka yari yazibye inda z'abo mu rugo rwa Abimeleki bose, abahora Sara umugore wa Aburahamu.
21:1 Uwiteka agenderera Sara nk'uko yavuze, Uwiteka agirira Sara ibyo yasezeranije. 
21:2  Sara asama inda ya Aburahamu ashaje, babyarana umuhungu igihe Imana yamubwiye kigeze. 
21:3 Aburahamu yita umuhungu yabyaye Isaka, uwo yabyaranye na Sara. 
21:4  Aburahamu akeba Isaka umuhungu we amaze iminsi munani avutse, uko Imana yamutegetse. 
21:5 Aburahamu yabyaye uwo muhungu we Isaka, amaze imyaka ijana avutse. 
21:6 Sara aravuga ati “Imana iranshekeje, abazabyumva bose bazasekana nanjye.” 
21:7  Ati “Ni nde uba warabwiye Aburahamu yuko Sara azonsa abana? Ko mubyariye umuhungu ashaje.”
21:8   Umwana arakura aracuka, ku munsi Isaka yacukiyeho Aburahamu ararika abantu benshi arabagaburira.
21:9 Sara abona umuhungu wa Hagari Umunyegiputakazi, uwo yabyaranye na Aburahamu, abaseka. 
21:10 Ni cyo cyatumye abwira Aburahamu ati “Senda uyu muja n'umuhungu we, kuko umuhungu w'uyu muja atazaraganwa n'umuhungu wanjye Isaka.” 
21:11  Ibyo by'uwo muhungu we bitera Aburahamu agahinda kenshi. 
21:12  Imana ibwira Aburahamu iti “We kugirira uwo muhungu agahinda n'umuja wawe, ibyo Sara akubwira byose umwumvire, kuko kuri Isaka ari ho urubyaro ruzakwitirirwa. 
21:13   Kandi umuhungu w'uwo muja na we nzamuhindura ubwoko, kuko ari urubyaro rwawe.”
21:14 Aburahamu azinduka kare kare, yenda umutsima n'imvumba y'uruhu irimo amazi, abiha Hagari abishyira ku rutugu rwe, amuha n'uwo mwana aramusenda, avayo azerera mu butayu bw'i Bērisheba. 
21:15 Ya mvumba ishiramo amazi, arambika umwana munsi y'igihuru cy'aho. 
21:16   Aragenda yicara amwerekeye, amuhaye intera nk'aho umuntu yarasa umwambi, kuko yibwiraga ati “Ne kureba umwana wanjye apfa.” Yicara amwerekeye atera hejuru ararira.
21:17 Imana yumva ijwi ry'uwo muhungu, marayika w'Imana ari mu ijuru, ahamagara Hagari aramubaza ati “Ubaye ute, Hagari? Witinya kuko Imana yumviye ijwi ry'uwo muhungu aho ari. 
21:18 Haguruka, byutsa umuhungu umufate mu maboko, kuko nzamuhindura ubwoko bukomeye.” 
21:19 Imana imuhumura amaso, abona iriba, aragenda avoma amazi yuzuye ya mvumba, ayaramiza umuhungu we. 
21:20 Nuko Imana ibana n'uwo muhungu arakura, atura mu butayu, aba umurashi. 
21:21   Aba mu butayu bw'i Parani, nyina amusabira Umunyegiputakazi.
21:22  Muri iyo minsi, Abimeleki na Fikoli umutware w'ingabo ze babwira Aburahamu bati “Imana iri kumwe nawe mu byo ukora byose. 
21:23   Nuko rero, undahire Imana yuko utazandiganya cyangwa umwana wanjye cyangwa umwuzukuru wanjye, ahubwo ineza nakugiriye ko uzayinyitura, jyewe n'igihugu wasuhukiyemo.”
21:24   Aburahamu aramusubiza ati “Ndarahira.”
21:25 Aburahamu azimuza Abimeleki ku by'iriba, abagaragu ba Abimeleki bamunyaze. 
21:26 Abimeleki aramusubiza ati “Sinzi uwakoze ibyo, nawe ntiwigeze kubimbwira, kandi sinigeze kubyumva keretse none.” 
21:27 Aburahamu azana intama n'inka, abiha Abimeleki, bombi barasezerana. 
21:28 Aburahamu arobanura abāgazi b'intama barindwi bo mu mukumbi we. 
21:29   Abimeleki abaza Aburahamu ati “Abo bāgazi b'intama barindwi urobanuye, bisobanuye iki?”
21:30 Aramusubiza ati “Aba bāgazi b'intama uko ari barindwi, ndabaguhera kugira ngo bimbere umugabo, yuko ari jye wafukuye iryo riba.” 
21:31   Ni cyo cyatumye yita aho hantu Bērisheba, kuko ari ho barahiriye bombi.
21:32 Nuko basezeranira i Bērisheba, Abimeleki ahagurukana na Fikoli umutware w'ingabo ze, basubira mu gihugu cy'Abafilisitiya. 
21:33 Aburahamu atera igiti cyitwa umwesheri i Bērisheba, yambarizayo izina ry'Uwiteka, Imana ihoraho. 
21:34 Aburahamu amara iminsi myinshi asuhukiye mu gihugu cy'Abafilisitiya.
22:1  Hanyuma y'ibyo, Imana igerageza Aburahamu iramuhamagara iti “Aburahamu.” Aritaba ati “Karame.” 
