22:18  Kandi mu rubyaro rwawe ni mo amahanga yose yo mu isi azaherwa umugisha kuko wanyumviye.” 
22:19   Aburahamu asubira aho abagaragu be bari, barahaguruka bajyana i Bērisheba, agezeyo arahatura.
22:20 Hanyuma y'ibyo babwira Aburahamu bati “Na Miluka yabyaranye na mwene so Nahori abana.” 
22:21 Imfura ye ni Usi, hakurikiraho Buzi murumuna we, na Kemuweli se wa Aramu, 
