23:6   “Databuja, utwumve uri umuntu ukomeye cyane muri twe, uhambe umupfu wawe mu mva yacu uri buhitemo muri zose, nta wo muri twe uri bukwime imva ye ngo we guhambamo umupfu wawe.”
23:7 Aburahamu arahaguruka, yikubita imbere ya bene igihugu, ni bo Baheti. 
