23:10 Efuroni yari yicaye hagati mu Baheti, Efuroni Umuheti asubiza Aburahamu, Abaheti bamwumva, abinjiraga mu irembo ry'umudugudu wabo bose ati 
23:11   “Ahubwo databuja, nyumva. Iyo sambu ndayiguhaye, n'ubuvumo burimo ndabuguhaye, mbiguhereye imbere y'ab'ubwoko bwacu, hamba umupfu wawe.”
23:12 Aburahamu yikubita imbere ya bene igihugu. 
23:13   Abwira Efuroni bene igihugu bamwumva ati “Ndakwinginze, nyumvira. Ndakwishyura igiciro cy'iyo sambu, cyemere nkiguhe, mpambemo umupfu wanjye.”
23:14 Efuroni asubiza Aburahamu ati 
