37:20 Nuko nimuze tumwice, tumujugunye mu rwobo rumwe muri izi zacukuriwe kubika amazi, tuzavuge tuti ‘Inyamaswa y'inkazi yaramuriye’, tuzamenya inzozi ze, uko zizaba.”
37:21 Rubeni arabyumva aramubakiza, arababwira ati “Twe kumuhwanya.” 
