38:10 Icyo yakoze icyo cyari kibi mu maso y'Uwiteka, na we aramwica. 
38:11 Maze Yuda abwira Tamari umukazana we ati “Guma mu nzu ya so uri umupfakazi, ugeze aho umwana wanjye Shela azakurira.” Kuko yibwiraga ati “Na we ye gupfa nka bene se.” Tamari aragenda, aguma mu nzu ya se.
38:12 Hashize iminsi, umukobwa wa Shuwa muka Yuda, arapfa. Yuda amaze kumwerera, arazamuka ajya i Timuna, aho abagaragu be bakemuriraga intama ze, we n'incuti ye Hira Umunyadulamu. 
38:13 Babwira Tamari bati “Sobukwe arazamutse, agiye i Timuna gukemuza intama ze.” 
38:14 Yiyambura imyenda y'ubupfakazi, yitwikira umwenda mu mutwe arisēsūra, yicara mu marembo ya Enayimu yo ku nzira ijya i Timuna, kuko yabonye Shela amaze gukura, ntibamumuhe ngo amuhungure.
38:15 Yuda amubonye agira ngo ni maraya, kuko yari yitwikiriye mu maso. 
38:16 Atambikira aho ari iruhande rw'inzira, aramubwira ati “Ndakwinginze turyamane.” Kuko yari atazi ko ari umukazana we.
38:17 Aramusubiza ati “Ndakoherereza umwana w'ihene wo mu mukumbi.”
38:18 Na we aramubaza ati “Ndaguha ngwate ki?”
38:19 Arahaguruka aragenda, yiyambura umwenda wo mu mutwe, yambara imyenda ye y'ubupfakazi.
38:20 Yuda yohereza wa mwana w'ihene, awuhaye wa Munyadulamu incuti ye, ngo uwo mugore amusubize za ngwate, aramubura. 
38:21 Abaza abagabo bo mu mudugudu yarimo ati “Maraya uwo ari he, wari Enayimu iruhande rw'inzira?”
38:22 Asubira aho Yuda ari aramubwira ati “Ntawe nabonye, kandi abaho bambwiye ngo ‘Nta maraya wari uhari.’ ”
38:23 Yuda aramusubiza ati “Nabyijyanire twe gukorwa n'isoni, dore nohereje uyu mwana w'ihene maze uramubura.”
38:24 Hashize amezi nk'atatu, babwira Yuda bati “Tamari umukazana wawe yarasambanye, kandi afite inda y'ubusambanyi.”
38:25 Bakimusohora atuma kuri sebukwe ati “Nyir'ibi bintu ni we wantwitse inda.” Kandi ati “Ndakwinginze, menya nyir'ibi: impeta iriho ikimenyetso n'imigozi yayo n'inkoni.”
38:26 Yuda yemera ko ari ibye ati “Andushije gukiranuka, kuko ntamuhaye Shela umwana wanjye.” Ntiyongera kuryamana na we ukundi.
38:27 Nuko mu iramukwa rye, impanga zari mu nda ye. 
38:28 Akiramukwa, umwe hahinguka igikonjo cye, umubyaza aragifata ahambiraho urudodo rutukura ati “Uyu ni we mpfura.” 
