42:1 Yakobo yumva yuko ubuhashyi buri muri Egiputa abaza abana be ati “Ni iki gituma murebana?” 
42:2  Kandi ati “Numvise yuko hari ubuhashyi muri Egiputa, nimumanuke mujyeyo muduhahireyo tubeho tudapfa.” 
42:3 Bene se wa Yosefu cumi baramanuka, bajya guhaha imyaka y'impeke muri Egiputa. 
42:4 Ariko Benyamini mwene nyina wa Yosefu, Yakobo ntiyamutumana na bene se, kuko yibwiraga ati “Ahari yagira ibyago.”
42:5 Abana ba Isirayeli bajya guhahana n'abandi, kuko inzara yateye mu gihugu cy'i Kanāni. 
42:6 Kandi Yosefu ni we wari umutware w'igihugu cya Egiputa, ni we wahahishaga abo muri icyo gihugu bose. Bene se wa Yosefu baraza, bamwikubita imbere bubamye. 
42:7 Yosefu abona bene se arabamenya, arabirengagiza, ababwira nabi. Arababaza ati “Murava he?”
42:8 Yosefu amenya bene se ariko bo ntibamumenya. 
42:9  Yosefu yibuka za nzozi yabaroteye arababwira ati “Muri abatasi muje gutata aho igihugu gifite amaboko make.” 
42:10 Baramusubiza bati “Si ko biri databuja, ahubwo abagaragu bawe tuzanywe no guhaha. 
42:11 Twese tuva inda imwe, turi abanyakuri, abagaragu bawe ntituri abatasi.”
42:12 Arababwira ati “Si ko biri, ahubwo gutata aho igihugu gifite amaboko make ni ko kubazanye.”
42:13 Baramusubiza bati “Abagaragu bawe turi abavandimwe turi cumi na babiri, turi abana b'umwe wo mu gihugu cy'i Kanāni, umuhererezi yasigaranye na data, undi ntakiriho.”
42:14 Yosefu arababwira ati “Icyo ni cyo nababwiye nti ‘Muri abatasi.’ 
42:15 Iki ni cyo kizabahakanira: ndahiye ubugingo bwa Farawo, ntimuzava hano umuhererezi wanyu ataje. 
42:16 Mutume umwe muri mwe azane murumuna wanyu, namwe murabohwa, amagambo yanyu ageragezwe yuko muri abanyakuri. Nibitaba bityo, ndahiye ubugingo bwa Farawo, muri abatasi.” 
42:17 Bose abamaza mu nzu y'imbohe iminsi itatu.
42:18 Ku munsi wa gatatu Yosefu arababwira ati “Mugenze mutya mudapfa kuko nubaha Imana: 
42:19 niba muri abanyakuri umwe muri mwe abavandimwe, asigare abohewe mu nzu yanyu y'imbohe, abandi mugende mujyane imyaka y'impeke yo kubamara inzara mu ngo zanyu, 
42:20 maze munzanire umuhererezi wanyu. Ni ho amagambo yanyu azamenyekana ko ari ay'ukuri, bigatuma mudapfa.”
42:21 Baravugana bati “Ni ukuri turiho urubanza rw'ibyo twagiriye mwene data, kuko twabonye uko umutima we wari ubabaye ubwo yatwingingaga natwe ntitumwumvire, ni byo biduteye aya makuba.”
42:22    Rubeni arababwira ati “Sinababwiye nti, mwe gukora icyaha kuri uwo mwana mukanga kunyumvira? Ni cyo gitumye amaraso ye adushakirwaho.”
42:23 Ntibamenya yuko Yosefu yumva ibyo bavuga, kuko yavugirwaga n'umusemyi. 
42:24 Abatera umugongo abasiga aho ararira, abagarukaho avugana na bo, abakuramo Simiyoni, amubohera mu maso yabo.
42:25 Yosefu ategeka ko babuzuriza imyaka y'impeke mu masaho yabo, kandi ngo basubize ifeza y'umuntu wese mu isaho ye, kandi babahe n'impamba. Babagirira batyo. 
42:26 Bahekesha indogobe zabo ihaho ryabo, bavayo. 
42:27 Aho baraye, umwe muri bo ahambuye isaho ye ngo agaburire indogobe ye, abona ifeza ye, asanga iri mu munwa w'isaho. 
42:28 Abwira bene se ati “Ifeza yanjye irangarukiye, dore iri mu isaho yanjye.” Bakuka imitima, barebana bahinda imishyitsi bati “Ibi ni ibiki, ibyo Imana itugiriye?”
42:29 Basohora kuri se Yakobo mu gihugu cy'i Kanāni, bamubwira ibyababayeho byose bati 
42:30 “Umugabo ukomeye utwara icyo gihugu, yatubwiye nabi akeka yuko turi abatasi babatata. 
42:31 Natwe turamubwira tuti ‘Turi abanyakuri, ntituri abatasi. 
42:32 Turi abavandimwe turi cumi na babiri dusangiye data umwe, umwe ntakiriho, umuhererezi yasigaranye na data mu gihugu cy'i Kanāni.’ 
42:33 Uwo mugabo ukomeye utwara icyo gihugu aratubwira ati ‘Iki ni cyo kizambwira ko muri abanyakuri: nimunsigire umwe muri mwe abavandimwe, mujyane ibyo kubamara inzara mu ngo zanyu, mugende 
42:34 munzanire umuhererezi wanyu. Ni ho nzamenya yuko mutari abatasi, ahubwo ko muri abanyakuri, nanjye nzabaha mwene so kandi muzatunda mu gihugu.’ ”
42:35 Basutse ibyo mu masaho yabo babona igipfunyika cy'ifeza cy'umuntu wese kiri mu isaho ye, bo na se babonye ibipfunyika byabo baratinya. 
42:36 Se Yakobo arababwira ati “Mungize incike: Yosefu ntakiriho, Simiyoni ntariho, none kandi murashaka kunkuraho na Benyamini! Ibyo ni jye bibayeho byose!”
42:37 Rubeni abwira se ati “Nintamukugarurira uzice abahungu banjye bombi, mumpe ndamwishingiye nzamukugarurira.”
42:38 Aramusubiza ati “Umwana wanjye ntazajyana namwe, kuko mwene nyina yapfuye akaba asigaye ari ikinege, yagirira ibyago mu nzira muzacamo, muzatuma imvi zanjye zimanukana ishavu zijya ikuzimu.”
43:1 Inzara irushaho kuba nyinshi mu gihugu. 
43:2 Bamaze imyaka y'impeke bakuye muri Egiputa, se arababwira ati “Nimusubireyo, muduhahire utwo kurya.” 
43:3 Yuda aramubwira ati “Wa mugabo yaratwihanangirije ati ‘Ntimuzance iryera mutazanye na murumuna wanyu.’ 
43:4 Watwoherezanya na murumuna wacu, twagenda tukaguhahirayo, 
43:5 ariko nutamwohereza ntitujyayo, kuko wa mugabo yatubwiye ati ‘Ntimuzance iryera mutazanye na murumuna wanyu.’ ”
43:6 Isirayeli arababaza ati “Ni iki cyatumye mungirira nabi mutyo, mukabwira uwo mugabo yuko mufite mwene so wundi?”
43:7 Baramusubiza bati “Uwo mugabo yatubajije atwinja, uko turi ubwacu, na bene wacu uko bari ati ‘Muracyafite so? Mufite mwene so wundi?’ Tumusubiza ibyo yatubajije. Tuba twarabwiwe n'iki yuko ari butubwire ati ‘Muzane murumuna wanyu’?”
43:8 Yuda abwira se Isirayeli ati “Nyoherezanya n'uwo muhungu turahaguruka tugende, tubeho tudapfana nawe n'abana bacu. 
43:9 Mbaye umwishingizi we abe ari jye uzamubaza, nintamukugarurira nkamugushyikiriza, nzaba ngukoreye icyaha kitazamvaho iteka. 
43:10 Iyo tudatinda, nzi yuko none tuba tugarutse ubwa kabiri.”
43:11 Se Isirayeli arababwira ati “Ubwo bimeze bityo nimugenze mutya: mujyane mu masaho yanyu imbuto zo muri iki gihugu ziruta izindi ubwiza muzishyīre uwo mugabo ho ituro, mujyane umuti womora muke n'ubuki buke, n'imibavu n'ishangi, n'ububemba n'indozi,</span><span class="note f"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body"><span class="fk">indozi </span><span class="ft"> ni imbuto zisa n'ububemba.
43:12 kandi mujyane ifeza z'ingereka zingana na zo, n'ifeza zagarutse mu minwa y'amasaho yanyu muzisubizeyo, ahari ni amahugwe yatumye zigaruka. 
43:13 Mujyane na murumuna wanyu muhaguruke musubire kuri uwo mugabo, 
43:14 Imana Ishoborabyose ibahe kubabarirwa na we ngo ababohorere mwene so wundi na Benyamini. Nanjye niba bikwiriye ko mba incike, nzabeyo.”
43:15 Ba bagabo benda ayo maturo, bajyana ifeza z'ingereka zingana na zo bajyana na Benyamini, barahaguruka baramanuka bajya muri Egiputa, bahagarara imbere ya Yosefu. 
43:16 Yosefu abonye Benyamini ari kumwe na bo, abwira igisonga cye ati “Injiza aba bantu mu nzu yanjye, ubage witegure ibyokurya, turi burīre hamwe ku manywa y'ihangu.” 
43:17 Uwo mugabo akora ibyo Yosefu yamutegetse, yinjiza abo bagabo mu nzu ya Yosefu.
43:18 Baratinya kuko yabinjije mu nzu ya Yosefu, baravuga bati “Ifeza zagarutse mu masaho yacu ubwo twazaga mbere, ni zo zatumye batwinjiza ngo adushakeho urwitwazo, adusumire, atunyagane n'indogobe zacu, tube imbata.” 
43:19 Begera cya gisonga cya Yosefu, bavuganira na cyo ku muryango bati 
43:20 “Databuja, mbere twaramanutse tuza guhaha, 
43:21 tugeze mu icumbi duhambura amasaho yacu, umuntu wese asanga ifeza ye iri mu munwa w'isaho ye, ifeza zacu dusanga zingana uko zanganaga none turazigaruye. 
43:22 Kandi tuzanye izindi feza zo guhaha, ntituzi uwashubije ifeza zacu mu masaho yacu.”
43:23 Arabasubiza ati “Mushyitse imitima mu nda ntimutinye, Imana yanyu, Imana ya so, ni yo yabashyiriye ubutunzi mu masaho, jyeweho ifeza zanyu narazishyikiriye.” Asohora Simiyoni aramubazanira.
43:24 Nuko wa mugabo yinjiza abo bagabo mu nzu ya Yosefu, abaha amazi boga ibirenge, agaburira n'indogobe zabo. 
43:25 Begeranya amaturo kugira ngo Yosefu naza ku manywa y'ihangu, asange biteguye kuyamutura, kuko bari bumvise yuko bari burīre hamwe na we. 
43:26 Yosefu atashye, bamusangisha mu nzu ya maturo bazanye, bamwikubita imbere bubamye. 
43:27 Ababaza uko bari, kandi ati “So aracyakoma, wa musaza mwavugaga? Aracyariho?”
43:28 Baramusubiza bati “Data, umugaragu wawe ni muzima, aracyariho.” Barunama bikubita hasi.
43:29 Yubura amaso abona Benyamini murumuna we, mwene nyina arababaza ati “Uwo ni we muhererezi wanyu mwambwiraga?” Maze aramubwira ati “Imana ikugirire neza, mwana wanjye.” 
43:30 Yosefu yihuta kugenda, kuko umutima we wari ufitiye urukumbuzi mwene nyina, ashaka aho aririra, yinjira mu nzu haruguru ayiririramo. 
43:31 Yiyuhagira mu maso aragaruka, ariyumanganya aravuga ati “Nimwarure ibyokurya.” 
43:32 Bamugaburira ukwe, na bene se babagaburira ukwabo, n'Abanyegiputa barīraga hamwe na we babagaburira ukwabo, kuko Abanyegiputa batasangiraga n'Abaheburayo, kuko cyari ikizira ku Banyegiputa. 
43:33 Bicara imbere ye, bicazwa uko bakurikirana, imfura uko ubukuru bwayo buri, n'umuhererezi uko ubuto bwe buri, bavugana batangara. 
43:34 Yosefu ategeka ko babazanira amagaburo yari imbere ye, ariko igaburo rya Benyamini riruta ayabo gatanu. Baranywa banezeranwa na we.
44:1 Yosefu ategeka igisonga cye ati “Nimwuzuze amasaho y'abo bagabo ihaho ringana n'iryo bashobora kujyana, ushyire n'ifeza y'umuntu mu munwa w'isaho ye. 
44:2 Ushyire n'igikombe cyanjye cy'ifeza mu munwa w'isaho y'umuhererezi, ushyiranemo n'ifeza ye yahahishaga.” Abigenza uko Yosefu yamutegetse. 
44:3 Bukeye hamaze kubona, abo bagabo basezeranwa n'indogobe zabo. 
44:4 Bavuye mu mudugudu bataragera kure, Yosefu abwira igisonga cye ati “Haguruka ukurikire ba bagabo, nubageraho ubabwire uti ‘Ni iki gitumye mwitura inabi uwabagiriye neza? 
44:5 Icyo mwibye si cyo databuja anywesha, kandi si cyo yikingira aragura? Ubwo mwakoze mutyo, mwakoze icyaha.’ ”
44:6 Abageraho, ababwira ayo magambo. 
44:7 Baramubwira bati “Databuja, ni iki kikuvugishije amagambo ameze atyo? Ntibikabeho ko abagaragu bawe dukora ibimeze bityo. 
44:8 Dore ifeza twasanze mu minwa y'amasaho yacu twarazigushubije, tuzivanye mu gihugu cy'i Kanāni. None twabasha dute kwiba ifeza cyangwa izahabu byo mu nzu ya shobuja? 
44:9 Uwo uri bukibonane wo mu bagaragu bawe yicwe, natwe duhinduke imbata zawe, databuja.”
44:10 Arababwira ati “Nuko rero bibe nk'uko mubivuze. Uwo kiri bubonekeho ni we uri bube imbata yanjye, namwe ntimuri bugibweho n'urubanza.” 
44:11 Barihuta barururutsa, umuntu wese ahambura isaho ye, 
44:12 arasaka ahēra ku mpfura ageza ku muhererezi, cya gikombe kiboneka mu isaho ya Benyamini. 
44:13 Bashishimura imyambaro yabo, umuntu wese ahekesha indogobe ye imitwaro, basubira mu mudugudu.
44:14 Yuda na bene se bagera mu nzu ya Yosefu, basanga akiri aho bamwikubita imbere. 
44:15 Yosefu arababaza ati “Icyo mukoze icyo ni igiki? Ntimuzi yuko umuntu umeze nkanjye ashobora kuragura koko?”
44:16 Yuda aramusubiza ati “Databuja, turagusubiza iki? Turavuga iki? Turireguza iki? Imana yamenye gukiranirwa kw'abagaragu bawe. Dore turi imbata zawe databuja, twe n'uwo cya gikombe kibonetseho.”
44:17 Aramusubiza ati “Ntibikabeho ko ngira ntyo: uwo igikombe kibonetseho ni we uri bube imbata yanjye, ariko mwe mwigendere mujye kwa so amahoro.”
44:18 Yuda aramwegera aramubwira ati “Databuja, ndakwinginze, jyewe umugaragu wawe reka mvugire ijambo mu matwi yawe, uburakari bwawe bwe kugurumanira umugaragu wawe, kuko uhwanye na Farawo rwose. 
44:19 Databuja, ntiwabajije abagaragu bawe uti ‘Muracyafite so, cyangwa hari undi mwene so mufite?’ 
44:20 Natwe tukagusubiza databuja tuti ‘Dufite data w'umusaza, hariho n'umwana yabyaye ashaje aracyari muto, mukuru we yarapfuye, ni we usigaye ari ikinege mu nda ya nyina, se aramukunda.’ 
44:21 Maze ukabwira twe abagaragu bawe uti ‘Muzamunzanire murebe.’ 
44:22 Tukakubwira databuja tuti ‘Uwo muhungu ntiyasiga se, yamusiga se yapfa.’ 
44:23 Nawe ukabwira twe abagaragu bawe uti ‘Umuhererezi wanyu nimutamanukana, ntimuzongere kunca iryera.’
44:24 “Nuko tuzamutse tugeze kuri data, umugaragu wawe, tumubwira amagambo yawe databuja. 
44:25 Data aratubwira ati ‘Nimwongere musubireyo, muduhahireyo utwo kurya.’ 
44:26 Turamusubiza tuti ‘Ntitwasubirayo. Umuhererezi wacu nitujyana tuzamanuka tujyeyo, kuko tutabasha guca uwo mugabo iryera, umuhererezi wacu tutari kumwe.’ 
44:27 Data, umugaragu wawe aratubwira ati ‘Muzi yuko umugore wanjye twabyaranye abahungu babiri, 
44:28 umwe akamvaho nkibwira ndashidikanya yuko yatanyaguwe n'inyamaswa nanjye nkaba ntakimubona, 
44:29 nimunkuraho n'uyu akagira ibyago, muzatuma imvi zanjye zimanukana ishavu zijya ikuzimu.’
44:30 “Nuko none najya kuri data umugaragu wawe tutari kumwe n'uwo muhungu, 
44:31 data akabona tutazanye yapfa, kuko ubugingo bwe bwiboshye ku bw'uwo muhungu, twebwe abagaragu bawe tukaba dutumye imvi za data umugaragu wawe, zimanukana ishavu zijya ikuzimu. 
44:32 Kuko jyewe umugaragu wawe nishingiye uwo muhungu kuri data nti ‘Nintamugushyikiriza, nzaba ngukoreye icyaha data, kitazamvaho iteka.’ 
44:33 Nuko none ndakwinginze, databuja, jyewe umugaragu wawe ngume mu cyimbo cy'uwo muhungu ndi imbata yawe, kandi uwo muhungu atahane na bene se. 
44:34 Nasubira nte ngo njye kuri data, ntari kumwe n'uwo muhungu? Ne kureba ibyago bizagera kuri data.”
45:1   Yosefu ananirwa kwiyumanganya imbere y'abo bahagararanye bose, ahubwo avuga cyane ati “Nimusohore abantu bose bambise.” Ntihagira umuntu uhagararana na Yosefu, yirondorera bene se
45:2 Atera hejuru ararira, Abanyegiputa barabyumva, abo mu nzu ya Farawo barabyumva. 
45:3 Yosefu abwira bene se ati “Ndi Yosefu. Data aracyariho?” Bene se bashaka icyo bamusubiza kirabura, kuko bahagaritswe imitima no kuba imbere ye. 
45:4 Yosefu abwira bene se ati “Ndabinginze nimunyegere.” Baramwegera aravuga ati “Ndi Yosefu mwene so, mwaguze ngo njyanwe muri Egiputa. 
45:5 None ntimubabare, ntimwirakaririre yuko mwanguze ngo nzanwe ino, kuko Imana ari yo yatumye mbabanziriza ngo nkize ubugingo bw'abantu. 
45:6 Inzara imaze imyaka ibiri mu gihugu, hasigaye indi myaka itanu, batazahingiramo ntibasaruriremo. 
45:7 Kandi Imana yatumye mbabanziriza ngo ibabesheho mugire icyo musiga mu isi, ibarokoze gukiza gukomeye. 
45:8 Nuko none si mwe mwanyohereje ino ahubwo ni Imana, kandi yangize nka se wa Farawo n'umutegeka w'urugo rwe rwose, n'umutware w'igihugu cya Egiputa cyose.
45:9   “Nimwihute, muzamuke mujye kuri data mumubwire muti ‘Umwana wawe Yosefu ngo tukubwire yuko Imana yamugize umutware wa Egiputa hose, manuka umusange ntutinde.
45:10 Kandi uzatura mu gihugu cy'i Gosheni, umube bugufi, wowe n'abana bawe n'abuzukuru bawe, n'imikumbi yawe n'amashyo yawe, n'ibyo ufite byose. 
45:11 Kandi ngo azakugerererayo, kuko hagisigaye imyaka itanu y'inzara, we gukenana n'inzu yawe n'ibyo ufite byose.’
45:12 “Kandi murirebera, na mwene mama Benyamini arirebera, yuko ari jye ubyikuriye mu kanwa. 
45:13 Kandi muzabwire data icyubahiro cyanjye cyose mfite muri Egiputa, muzamubwire ibyo mwabonye byose, kandi muzatebutse data mumuzane ino.”
45:14 Yosefu ahobera mwene nyina Benyamini, begamiranya amajosi ararira, Benyamini aririra ku ijosi rya Yosefu. 
45:15 Asoma bene se bose, abaririraho, nyuma bene se baganira na we.
45:16 Inkuru y'ibyo igera kwa Farawo yuko bene se wa Yosefu baje, binezeza Farawo n'abagaragu be cyane. 
45:17 Farawo abwira Yosefu ati “Bwira bene so ngo nimugenze mutya: muhekeshe indogobe zanyu imitwaro, mugende mujye mu gihugu cy'i Kanāni, 
45:18 muzane so n'abo mu ngo zanyu, muze iwe, ngo na we azabaha ibyiza byo mu gihugu cya Egiputa, muzarya ibirushaho kuba byiza byo mu gihugu. 
45:19 Ndagutegetse kubabwira uti ‘Nimugenze mutya: mujyane amagare yo mu gihugu cya Egiputa yo gushyiramo abana banyu bato n'abagore banyu, muzane na so, muze ino. 
45:20 Kandi ntimwite ku bintu byanyu, kuko ibyiza byo mu gihugu cya Egiputa cyose ari ibyanyu.’ ”
45:21 Abana ba Isirayeli babigenza batyo. Yosefu abaha amagare nk'uko Farawo yategetse, abaha n'impamba. 
45:22 Kandi uko bangana, aha umuntu wese imyenda yo gukuranwa, ariko aha Benyamini ibice by'ifeza magana atatu, amuha n'imyenda yo gukuranwa gatanu. 
45:23 Na se amwoherereza izi ntashyo: indogobe cumi zihetse ibyiza bya Egiputa, n'indogobe z'ingore cumi zihetse imyaka y'impeke, n'imitsima n'ibyokurya bindi by'impamba bya se. 
45:24 Nuko asezerera bene se, bagenda ababwiye ati “Mwirinde, ntimutonganire mu nzira.”
45:25 Bava muri Egiputa barazamuka, bagera mu gihugu cy'i Kanāni kuri se Yakobo. 
45:26 Baramubwira bati “Yosefu aracyariho, ni we mutware w'igihugu cya Egiputa cyose.” Yakobo arakakara kuko atabemereye
45:27 Bamubwira amagambo yose Yosefu yabatumye. Abonye ya magare Yosefu yohereje kumuhagurutsa, umutima wa se wabo Yakobo urahembūka, 
45:28 Isirayeli aravuga ati “Ni byo bizi! Yosefu umwana wanjye aracyariho, ndajya kubonana na we ntarapfa.”
46:1 Isirayeli aragenda, ajyana ibyo atunze byose agera i Bērisheba, atambirayo ibitambo Imana ya se Isaka. 
46:2 Imana ihamagara Isirayeli mu iyerekwa rya nijoro iti “Yakobo, Yakobo!”
46:3 Iramubwira iti “Ndi Imana, Imana ya so. Ntutinye kumanuka ngo ujye muri Egiputa, kuko ari ho nzakugirira ishyanga rikomeye. 
46:4 Ubwanjye nzajyana nawe muri Egiputa, kandi ubwanjye ni jye uzagukūrayo, kandi Yosefu ni we uzahumbya amaso yawe.”
46:5 Yakobo arahaguruka ava i Bērisheba, abana ba Isirayeli bajyana Yakobo se n'abana babo bato, n'abagore babo mu magare Farawo yohereje kumuzana. 
46:6  Bajyana amatungo yabo n'ibintu byabo baronkeye mu gihugu cy'i Kanāni bajya muri Egiputa, Yakobo n'urubyaro rwe rwose rujyana na we: 
46:7 abahungu be n'abuzukuru be b'abahungu, n'abakobwa be n'abakobwa b'abahungu be, n'urubyaro rwe rwose rujyana na we muri Egiputa.
46:8 Aya ni yo mazina y'Abisirayeli bagiye muri Egiputa: Yakobo n'abahungu be, imfura ye ni Rubeni. 
46:9 Bene Rubeni ni Henoki na Palu, na Hesironi na Karumi. 
46:10 Bene Simiyoni ni Yemuweli na Yamini, na Ohadi na Yakini, na Sohari na Shawuli umwana w'Umunyakanānikazi. 
46:11 Bene Lewi ni Gerushoni na Kohati na Merari. 
46:12 Bene Yuda ni Eri na Onani, na Shela na Perēsi na Zera, ariko Eri na Onani bapfiriye mu gihugu cy'i Kanāni. Bene Perēsi ni Hesironi na Hamuli. 
46:13 Bene Isakari ni Tola na Puwa, na Yobu na Shimuroni. 
46:14 Bene Zebuluni ni Seredi na Eloni na Yahilēli. 
46:15 Abo ni bo bene Leya yabyaraniye na Yakobo i Padanaramu, kandi babyarana n'umukobwa Dina. Abahungu be n'abakobwa be bose ni mirongo itatu na batatu.
46:16 Bene Gadi ni Sifiyoni na Hagi, na Shuni na Esiboni na Eri, na Arodi na Areli. 
46:17 Bene Asheri ni Imuna na Ishiva, na Ishivi na Beriya, na mushiki wabo Sera. Bene Beriya ni Heberi na Malikiyeli. 
